FBIS4-46371 "jptot024__l94048" JPRS-TOT-94-024-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 10 June 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA PALESTINIAN AFFAIRS Rafah Youth Wounded While Assembling Bomb Rafah Youth Wounded While Assembling Bomb TA1006071894 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in English 0400 GMT 10 Jun 94 TA1006071894 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el English BFN [Text] A Palestinian youth from the Arab village of Rafah was seriously wounded last night when a homemade explosive device he was holding blew up. He was taken to hospital in Jerusalem. Another youth was lightly hurt. Elsewhere, an IDF [Israel Defense Forces] patrol along the border with the Gaza autonomous area was fired on from the direction of the Khan Yunus refugee camp. The soldiers returned fire, apparently wounding two Palestinians.
